        <div class="how-it-works">
            <h4>🔍 Why Parameterized Queries Work</h4>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <div class="step-text"><strong style="color:#e0e0e0">Query structure is sent first.</strong> The database compiles and understands the SQL template before any user data is involved. The <code style="color:#4ec9b0">?</code> placeholder marks where data will go.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
